Available locations in the FluSight Hub

Source: R/data.R
hub_locations_flusight.Rd

Data set with available locations for the FluSight hub

hub_locations_flusight

Format

A data frame with 54 rows and 4 columns:

fips

FIPS code

location_name

Name of the location

abbreviation

Location abbreviation

population

Location population
